gomodel:SYNGO_3819  a     owl:Ontology ;
        rdfs:comment      "Rationale: Figure 4B: \"Approximately half of the presynaptic dendritic terminals of mitral cells, identified by vGlut1 staining, were positive for Syt10 (47% ± 11%, n = 3 mice; Figures 4E, 4F, and S5), suggesting that a considerable proportion of Syt10-containing vesicles that mediate IGF1 exocytosis in mitral cells are in close proximity to reciprocal M-G-M synapses.\". Experimental description: \"Adult mice (age between 3 to 5 months old) with or without prior viral injections were used \"" ;
        lego:modelstate   "production" ;
        dc:contributor    "https://orcid.org/0000-0003-0593-3443" , "https://orcid.org/0000-0002-2286-1587" , "https://orcid.org/0000-0002-2514-0216" ;
        dc:date           "2018-06-27" ;
